00:23:34,291 --> 00:23:35,333
[NAGASUMI] A harsh
reality confronts us

565
00:23:35,416 --> 00:23:36,875
when we return
from our field trip.

566
00:23:36,958 --> 00:23:39,541
Behold, a story of families
who seek and are hurt by love!

567
00:23:39,625 --> 00:23:41,791
As a father and a man,
